messages.messageBody:
REGISTRATION IS NOW OPEN!
Please visit the website www.unschoolerswaterparkgathering.com to register for the 6th Annual Unschoolers Waterpark Gathering in Sandusky, Ohio, February 3rd, 2013 to February 8th, 2013. Early bird price is only $35 per family. And the Kalahari Resort is offering early bird bonuses as well, a gift card, arcade passes and mini golf passes, if you reserve your room before October 31st. Also check out our speakers page to see information about our keynote speaker this year! AND, please share this post with other unschooling folks!
